<font color="yellow">You better not. You better not call Elder!</font>

611
00:41:13,509 --> 00:41:14,793
<font color="yellow">Why are you getting angry?</font>

612
00:41:15,454 --> 00:41:17,584
<font color="yellow">Are you getting angry because I'll tell him</font>

