00:43:19,290 --> 00:43:21,579
<font color="yellow">You need to get proper help from a real estate agent.</font>

635
00:43:22,048 --> 00:43:25,102
<font color="yellow">Many people become conned because they try to save money like you.</font>

636
00:43:25,642 --> 00:43:28,314
<font color="yellow">Mr. Detective, please help me out.</font>

637
00:43:28,977 --> 00:43:31,850
<font color="yellow">That money was all I had.</font>

638
00:43:32,931 --> 00:43:36,322
<font color="yellow">Gosh. People should help each other out, not con each other like this.</font>

639
00:43:37,431 --> 00:43:39,786
<font color="yellow">Then sue your friend first.</font>

640
00:43:40,915 --> 00:43:41,915
<font color="yellow">Sue?</font>

641
00:43:41,940 --> 00:43:44,613
<font color="yellow">You need to sue her so that we can catch her.</font>

642
00:43:46,485 --> 00:43:49,455
<font color="yellow">First, hire a lawyer, and go through the lawsuit process.</font>

643
00:43:50,579 --> 00:43:51,579
<font color="yellow">Sir...</font>

644
00:44:05,001 --> 00:44:09,871
<font color="yellow">Chung-ja! My daughter! This time, it is really unfair for me!</font>

645
00:44:10,321 --> 00:44:11,321
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

646
00:44:11,642 --> 00:44:12,727
<font color="yellow">Who are you?</font>

647
00:44:13,384 --> 00:44:15,363
<font color="yellow">I'm Chung-ja's friend, Hwang Geum-sil.</font>

648
00:44:16,157 --> 00:44:19,301
<font color="yellow">Long time ago when I visited your home, you used to make pancakes for me.</font>

649
00:44:19,907 --> 00:44:21,239
<font color="yellow">I did?</font>

650
00:44:21,265 --> 00:44:24,566
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear. I'm getting old now. I can't remember very well.</font>

651
00:44:24,798 --> 00:44:26,144
<font color="yellow">That happens when you get old.</font>

652
00:44:26,245 --> 00:44:29,297
<font color="yellow">You can't remember people because you're getting old,</font>

653
00:44:29,985 --> 00:44:32,678
<font color="yellow">but how can you remember those flower cards so well?</font>

654
00:44:32,868 --> 00:44:34,001
<font color="yellow">What did you say?</font>

655
00:44:36,079 --> 00:44:37,819
<font color="yellow">She's so mean like this.</font>

656
00:44:38,353 --> 00:44:41,517
<font color="yellow">She doesn't treat me very well.</font>

657
00:44:41,907 --> 00:44:45,472
<font color="yellow">I was dragged to the police station when I didn't do anything wrong, and</font>

658
00:44:45,498 --> 00:44:48,916
<font color="yellow">she doesn't pity me when I'm suffering. All she does is act like this!</font>

659
00:44:48,941 --> 00:44:51,813
<font color="yellow">Do you think our country's policemen have nothing better to</font>

660
00:44:52,415 --> 00:44:54,946
<font color="yellow">do than to catch innocent people and lock them up in jail?</font>

661
00:44:55,087 --> 00:44:59,587
<font color="yellow">Ms. Chun, my son will take care of everything, so just wait a little bit.</font>

662
00:45:01,149 --> 00:45:02,682
<font color="yellow">Hello. I'm Lee Jang-go.</font>

663
00:45:02,844 --> 00:45:05,680
<font color="yellow">You're very handsome!</font>

664
00:45:06,290 --> 00:45:08,118
<font color="yellow">Jang-go, what does she need to do now?</font>

665
00:45:09,680 --> 00:45:12,976
<font color="yellow">Just wait here for a moment. Let me go meet the detective-in-charge.</font>

666
00:45:13,314 --> 00:45:14,495
<font color="yellow">Don't worry too much.</font>

667
00:45:17,017 --> 00:45:18,876
<font color="yellow">My son is a lawyer.</font>

