685
00:47:02,649 --> 00:47:03,649
<font color="yellow">Yes, ma'am.</font>

686
00:47:04,274 --> 00:47:07,267
<font color="yellow">But I have work to do, so I have to leave first.</font>

687
00:47:07,501 --> 00:47:08,696
<font color="yellow">Yes, go on!</font>

688
00:47:09,860 --> 00:47:11,060
<font color="yellow">Thank you so much.</font>

689
00:47:11,665 --> 00:47:13,524
<font color="yellow">You must be busy, but you helped us out.</font>

690
00:47:14,626 --> 00:47:16,209
<font color="yellow">I'll call you.</font>

691
00:47:16,657 --> 00:47:17,657
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

692
00:47:18,040 --> 00:47:19,443
<font color="yellow">See you at home.</font>

693
00:47:20,001 --> 00:47:21,068
<font color="yellow">-Bye, mom. -Bye.</font>

694
00:47:29,411 --> 00:47:32,216
<font color="yellow">Let me make myself clear. This is definitely the end!</font>

695
00:47:33,200 --> 00:47:36,763
<font color="yellow">Even if you use Elder to threaten me, it won't work!</font>

696
00:47:38,021 --> 00:47:40,051
<font color="yellow">This is so embarrassing!</font>

697
00:47:41,092 --> 00:47:43,623
<font color="yellow">How can you humiliate me in front of my friend and her son?</font>

698
00:47:44,778 --> 00:47:47,640
<font color="yellow">From now on, don't contact me even if you die.</font>

699
00:47:51,193 --> 00:47:52,865
<font color="yellow">Geum-sil, I'm sorry.</font>

700
00:47:54,231 --> 00:47:55,231
<font color="yellow">I'll call you later.</font>

701
00:47:56,536 --> 00:47:57,747
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

702
00:48:00,544 --> 00:48:03,741
<font color="yellow">Fine! I don't need a daughter like you either!</font>

703
00:48:05,294 --> 00:48:10,556
<font color="yellow">If I look for you again, I'll become your daughter, you brat.</font>

704
00:48:13,568 --> 00:48:15,932
<font color="yellow">It's been a while since we met again, but all I did</font>

