00:48:16,198 --> 00:48:18,334
<font color="yellow">was trouble you. I'll pay you back later, okay?</font>

706
00:48:19,465 --> 00:48:20,715
<font color="yellow">-Okay. -Bye.</font>

707
00:48:20,740 --> 00:48:21,740
<font color="yellow">Good-bye.</font>

708
00:48:43,958 --> 00:48:44,958
<font color="yellow">Seung-hee!</font>

709
00:48:45,341 --> 00:48:49,302
<font color="yellow">Mommy!</font>

710
00:48:51,880 --> 00:48:54,958
<font color="yellow">Yoo-sung, it's okay. There, there. It's all right.</font>

711
00:48:55,747 --> 00:48:57,991
<font color="yellow">Mom, what happened?</font>

712
00:48:59,294 --> 00:49:00,844
<font color="yellow">Where did the moving center man go?</font>

713
00:49:02,068 --> 00:49:05,486
<font color="yellow">He had other things to move, so he just left us.</font>

714
00:49:12,560 --> 00:49:13,791
<font color="yellow">He's too much.</font>

715
00:49:16,646 --> 00:49:20,712
<font color="yellow">What are we supposed to do if he just leaves our things here?</font>

716
00:49:32,302 --> 00:49:33,502
<font color="yellow">It's raining, too.</font>

717
00:49:35,419 --> 00:49:37,363
<font color="yellow">What do we do now?</font>

718
00:50:01,122 --> 00:50:05,013
<font color="yellow">Did the center deposit their money?</font>

719
00:50:06,364 --> 00:50:09,278
<font color="yellow">Yes, sir. They deposited two hundred thousand dollars today.</font>

720
00:50:10,176 --> 00:50:12,722
<font color="yellow">That's why they wanted to call the reporters,</font>

721
00:50:12,747 --> 00:50:15,015
<font color="yellow">take photos, and release an article, too.</font>

722
00:50:15,943 --> 00:50:16,943
<font color="yellow">Tell them no.</font>

723
00:50:18,193 --> 00:50:19,193
<font color="yellow">Yes, sir.</font>

724
00:50:32,622 --> 00:50:33,622
<font color="yellow">Hello!</font>

725
00:50:34,700 --> 00:50:35,700
<font color="yellow">Who is he?</font>

726
00:50:35,725 --> 00:50:38,110
<font color="yellow">He's the lawyer of the law firm in room 305.</font>

727
00:50:39,050 --> 00:50:40,944
<font color="yellow">Oh, you're a young one.</font>

728
00:50:41,633 --> 00:50:45,175
<font color="yellow">Work hard and pay your rent on time.</font>

729
00:50:45,934 --> 00:50:46,934
<font color="yellow">Yes, sir!</font>

730
00:50:47,286 --> 00:50:48,286
<font color="yellow">I'll work hard!</font>

731
00:50:48,528 --> 00:50:49,528
<font color="yellow">Good.</font>

