00:51:41,153 --> 00:51:43,020
<font color="yellow">I'm so sick and tired of it.</font>

734
00:51:52,020 --> 00:51:54,466
<font color="yellow">Mom, this won't do.</font>

735
00:51:55,419 --> 00:51:58,980
<font color="yellow">If it keeps raining, Yoo-sung might catch a cold.</font>

736
00:51:59,333 --> 00:52:01,321
<font color="yellow">You and Yoo-sung should go to a motel.</font>

737
00:52:01,896 --> 00:52:04,251
<font color="yellow">I have money for a motel.</font>

738
00:52:06,208 --> 00:52:07,208
<font color="yellow">I...</font>

739
00:52:10,708 --> 00:52:13,003
<font color="yellow">hate your father so much.</font>

740
00:52:15,583 --> 00:52:16,916
<font color="yellow">I can't forgive him.</font>

741
00:52:19,817 --> 00:52:22,122
<font color="yellow">How can he make us like this...</font>

742
00:52:24,435 --> 00:52:25,955
<font color="yellow">and die by himself?</font>

743
00:52:27,755 --> 00:52:29,209
<font color="yellow">Is death all there is to it?</font>

744
00:52:30,247 --> 00:52:31,247
<font color="yellow">Mom.</font>

745
00:52:32,317 --> 00:52:34,215
<font color="yellow">Why would you say that?</font>

746
00:52:34,505 --> 00:52:35,505
<font color="yellow">Fine.</font>

747
00:52:37,153 --> 00:52:38,989
<font color="yellow">There's nothing to it.</font>

748
00:52:41,582 --> 00:52:42,582
<font color="yellow">Seung-hee.</font>

749
00:52:43,333 --> 00:52:46,724
<font color="yellow">The three of us should end it here.</font>

750
00:52:48,708 --> 00:52:49,708
<font color="yellow">Mom.</font>

751
00:52:51,294 --> 00:52:52,501
<font color="yellow">What are you saying?</font>

752
00:52:52,934 --> 00:52:59,102
<font color="yellow">What's the point of living a worthless life that's lower than dirt?</font>

753
00:52:59,739 --> 00:53:01,219
<font color="yellow">Mom, what's wrong with you?</font>

754
00:53:02,200 --> 00:53:03,695
<font color="yellow">Don't be like this. Please!</font>

755
00:53:06,052 --> 00:53:11,970
<font color="yellow">I can't handle this any longer!</font>

756
00:53:13,435 --> 00:53:15,717
<font color="yellow">The three of us should just die together.</font>

757
00:53:16,544 --> 00:53:22,387
<font color="yellow">We can go meet your brother and your father.</font>

758
00:53:23,607 --> 00:53:24,607
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with you?</font>

759
00:53:25,685 --> 00:53:27,170
<font color="yellow">No matter how hard life is,</font>

760
00:53:28,450 --> 00:53:30,127
<font color="yellow">you shouldn't say that to me.</font>

761
00:53:31,267 --> 00:53:33,304
<font color="yellow">We worked so hard to come this far!</font>

762
00:53:35,333 --> 00:53:40,371
<font color="yellow">We survived when that wench Kang Mi-Jung fled with our money.</font>

763
00:53:41,466 --> 00:53:45,294
<font color="yellow">We survived when we had to beg on the streets in China.</font>

764
00:53:46,724 --> 00:53:49,301
<font color="yellow">We even survived...</font>

765
00:53:52,161 --> 00:53:55,161
<font color="yellow">when we saw father and brother being shot to death in front of our eyes.</font>

766
00:53:56,693 --> 00:53:59,943
<font color="yellow">But now you want to give up?</font>

767
00:54:01,114 --> 00:54:03,614
<font color="yellow">Seung-hee, I...</font>

768
00:54:06,482 --> 00:54:09,122
<font color="yellow">feel like this is all just a dream.</font>

769
00:54:10,731 --> 00:54:13,216
<font color="yellow">A nightmare that I won't be able to wake up from unless I die.</font>

770
00:54:14,107 --> 00:54:15,822
<font color="yellow">Mom, this isn't a dream.</font>

771
00:54:16,755 --> 00:54:17,829
<font color="yellow">This isn't a dream.</font>

772
00:54:18,778 --> 00:54:21,311
<font color="yellow">This is reality that we must overcome!</font>

773
00:54:22,333 --> 00:54:23,465
<font color="yellow">Seung-hee...</font>

