00:54:23,490 --> 00:54:26,137
<font color="yellow">Mom, what did dad say?</font>

775
00:54:27,021 --> 00:54:30,964
<font color="yellow">He told us that we had to live no matter what!</font>

776
00:54:32,497 --> 00:54:33,497
<font color="yellow">We can do this.</font>

777
00:54:34,435 --> 00:54:35,825
<font color="yellow">We can survive through this.</font>

778
00:54:38,732 --> 00:54:39,770
<font color="yellow">Seung-hee.</font>

779
00:54:40,888 --> 00:54:41,888
<font color="yellow">Mom.</font>

780
00:55:35,653 --> 00:55:36,653
<font color="yellow">Soon-ok!</font>

