00:57:46,755 --> 00:57:50,678
<font color="yellow">I can't go! I'll never go until I hear that song!</font>

791
00:57:50,990 --> 00:57:52,107
<font color="yellow">Stay here by yourself.</font>

792
00:57:52,451 --> 00:57:54,435
<font color="yellow">Don't ask me for help even when a ghost appears.</font>

793
00:58:05,264 --> 00:58:06,849
<font color="yellow">-It's a ghost! -It's a ghost!</font>

794
00:58:06,874 --> 00:58:07,874
<font color="yellow">Help!</font>

795
00:58:51,475 --> 00:58:55,165
<font color="yellow">Come on now. How can you do this in a park?</font>

796
00:58:57,803 --> 00:58:59,956
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry. We have nowhere else to go.</font>

797
00:59:00,521 --> 00:59:02,159
<font color="yellow">We'll go as soon as we get a place.</font>

798
00:59:02,482 --> 00:59:05,330
<font color="yellow">-Please let it slide. -If we could, we would.</font>

799
00:59:05,560 --> 00:59:09,927
<font color="yellow">We're getting complaints that someone set up a home underneath the bridge.</font>

800
00:59:11,053 --> 00:59:12,053
<font color="yellow">Excuse me! Hold on!</font>

801
00:59:13,396 --> 00:59:14,396
<font color="yellow">Mr. Jung?</font>

802
00:59:14,795 --> 00:59:17,514
<font color="yellow">Oh, hi mister!</font>

