00:59:19,029 --> 00:59:21,191
<font color="yellow">I'll take care of this matter.</font>

805
00:59:21,927 --> 00:59:24,591
<font color="yellow">-(Home of Free Immigrants. Name: Jung Woo-Jin.) Don't worry.</font>

