00:59:26,568 --> 00:59:28,110
<font color="yellow">Then we'll leave it up to you.</font>

807
00:59:36,912 --> 00:59:38,045
<font color="yellow">Ms. Kim Mi-poong,</font>

808
00:59:38,592 --> 00:59:41,407
<font color="yellow">why didn't you contact me when things have become so terrible for you?</font>

809
00:59:41,896 --> 00:59:44,606
<font color="yellow">I felt so bad that you always had to help us.</font>

