00:59:44,631 --> 00:59:47,487
<font color="yellow">My goodness. Why would you feel bad about this?</font>

811
00:59:47,951 --> 00:59:51,227
<font color="yellow">It's my job to make sure you and your family live well in this country.</font>

812
00:59:51,709 --> 00:59:55,516
<font color="yellow">Anyways, I found a temporary place for you to live in, so let's go there first.</font>

