815
01:00:46,654 --> 01:00:48,139
<font color="yellow">Sorry for troubling you.</font>

816
01:00:48,717 --> 01:00:49,978
<font color="yellow">It's no trouble at all.</font>

817
01:00:50,275 --> 01:00:51,896
<font color="yellow">It's an empty storage room anyways.</font>

818
01:00:52,350 --> 01:00:53,561
<font color="yellow">Is Mr. Kim in today?</font>

819
01:00:53,967 --> 01:00:55,177
<font color="yellow">I would like to say hi.</font>

820
01:00:55,482 --> 01:00:56,912
<font color="yellow">He's not here today.</font>

821
01:00:57,560 --> 01:00:59,467
<font color="yellow">I'll tell him you said hi.</font>

822
01:00:59,998 --> 01:01:00,998
<font color="yellow">Yes, thank you.</font>

823
01:01:07,326 --> 01:01:08,909
<font color="yellow">I heard your story from Mr. Jung.</font>

824
01:01:09,725 --> 01:01:11,560
<font color="yellow">How did something so terrible happen to you?</font>

825
01:01:12,631 --> 01:01:15,770
<font color="yellow">You can stay here comfortably until you find a new home.</font>

826
01:01:17,498 --> 01:01:19,425
<font color="yellow">I don't know how we can pay you back.</font>

827
01:01:20,170 --> 01:01:21,913
<font color="yellow">Thank you so much.</font>

828
01:01:26,209 --> 01:01:27,209
<font color="yellow">Hi.</font>

829
01:01:31,592 --> 01:01:32,592
<font color="yellow">Go on in.</font>

830
01:01:49,201 --> 01:01:50,201
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

831
01:01:51,498 --> 01:01:56,177
<font color="yellow">She did seem a bit immature, but she was bright and pretty.</font>

832
01:02:00,850 --> 01:02:02,450
<font color="yellow">Speaking of the devil...</font>

833
01:02:03,779 --> 01:02:04,779
<font color="yellow">Hi, Chung-ja.</font>

834
01:02:05,225 --> 01:02:08,895
<font color="yellow">I'm so grateful about yesterday that I think I should pay you back.</font>

835
01:02:09,537 --> 01:02:13,560
<font color="yellow">Come on. You don't need to pay me back when we're friends.</font>

836
01:02:14,115 --> 01:02:16,444
<font color="yellow">It's because I'm grateful and sorry to you.</font>

837
01:02:18,021 --> 01:02:19,885
<font color="yellow">Then buy my son dinner.</font>

838
01:02:20,943 --> 01:02:23,287
<font color="yellow">Tomorrow? Sure, that's fine.</font>

839
01:02:24,451 --> 01:02:28,474
<font color="yellow">My son won't have any fun eating with just you and me.</font>

840
01:02:29,216 --> 01:02:32,234
<font color="yellow">Your daughter seems to have a bright personality. Bring her out with you.</font>

841
01:02:33,404 --> 01:02:34,994
<font color="yellow">Okay. See you tomorrow.</font>

842
01:02:38,623 --> 01:02:39,623
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

843
01:02:40,201 --> 01:02:41,201
<font color="yellow">I did well.</font>

844
01:02:41,896 --> 01:02:44,974
<font color="yellow">I'm going to make Hee-Ra into Jang-go's wife.</font>

845
01:02:45,928 --> 01:02:50,186
<font color="yellow">If Jang-go gets support from wealthy in-laws, he'll be able to thrive in his work.</font>

846
01:02:50,779 --> 01:02:53,732
<font color="yellow">It'll be good for Chung-ja since they'll have a lawyer as a son-in-law.</font>

847
01:02:54,420 --> 01:03:00,324
<font color="yellow">I'm going to create a sturdy support system for Jang-go.</font>

848
01:03:09,357 --> 01:03:12,181
<font color="yellow">Mom, lie down.</font>

849
01:03:14,381 --> 01:03:18,693
<font color="yellow">Yes. This is a much better place than under that bridge.</font>

850
01:03:23,873 --> 01:03:25,253
<font color="yellow">But Yoo-sung, what's wrong?</font>

851
01:03:25,624 --> 01:03:28,568
<font color="yellow">Aunt, does this mean I can't go to kindergarten anymore?</font>

852
01:03:29,029 --> 01:03:30,993
<font color="yellow">Why not? You can go.</font>

853
01:03:31,724 --> 01:03:33,903
<font color="yellow">It's too far from here.</font>

854
01:03:34,581 --> 01:03:36,996
<font color="yellow">It's not far at all.</font>

855
01:03:37,576 --> 01:03:39,568
<font color="yellow">If you ride a bus, you'll be there in no time.</font>

856
01:03:39,865 --> 01:03:45,595
<font color="yellow">Grandma and I will take you to kindergarten every day.</font>

857
01:03:45,975 --> 01:03:46,975
<font color="yellow">Really?</font>

858
01:03:47,209 --> 01:03:48,553
<font color="yellow">Of course!</font>

859
01:03:49,404 --> 01:03:52,109
<font color="yellow">Yoo-sung, stay here with grandma.</font>

860
01:03:55,639 --> 01:03:56,972
<font color="yellow">Where are you going?</font>

861
01:03:57,459 --> 01:04:03,025
<font color="yellow">Well, I saw a law office on the third floor of this building.</font>

862
01:04:03,693 --> 01:04:06,611
<font color="yellow">I want to ask if there's a way I can get my money back.</font>

863
01:04:08,545 --> 01:04:11,606
<font color="yellow">We need to get our money back, mom.</font>

864
01:04:21,881 --> 01:04:25,556
<font color="yellow">Ms. Lawyer, that security deposit is money that we</font>

865
01:04:25,581 --> 01:04:29,372
<font color="yellow">saved over the year while not eating and not shopping.</font>

866
01:04:29,912 --> 01:04:30,912
<font color="yellow">Please.</font>

867
01:04:31,357 --> 01:04:33,417
<font color="yellow">Please help me get that money back.</font>

868
01:04:34,482 --> 01:04:35,867
<font color="yellow">That's so pitiful.</font>

869
01:04:36,435 --> 01:04:39,367
<font color="yellow">All right. We'll be able to come up with a way together.</font>

870
01:04:40,649 --> 01:04:43,122
<font color="yellow">Thank you! Thank you, Ms. Lawyer!</font>

871
01:04:44,451 --> 01:04:46,776
<font color="yellow">But I'm not a lawyer.</font>

872
01:04:47,596 --> 01:04:48,596
<font color="yellow">Excuse me?</font>

873
01:04:49,779 --> 01:04:50,951
<font color="yellow">You're not a lawyer?</font>

874
01:04:52,029 --> 01:04:54,326
<font color="yellow">Isn't this a law firm?</font>

875
01:04:55,013 --> 01:05:00,143
<font color="yellow">This is a law firm, but the lawyer is away for the moment. I'm the office manager.</font>

876
01:05:00,896 --> 01:05:02,404
<font color="yellow">If you wait here for a moment-</font>

877
01:05:04,498 --> 01:05:06,794
<font color="yellow">Speaking of the devil. He came right on time.</font>

878
01:05:08,600 --> 01:05:09,800
<font color="yellow">You have a client.</font>

879
01:05:11,740 --> 01:05:12,740
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

880
01:05:13,021 --> 01:05:14,977
<font color="yellow">What brings you here?</font>

881
01:05:18,826 --> 01:05:21,162
<font color="yellow">She lost her entire security deposit.</font>

882
01:05:28,095 --> 01:05:31,553
<font color="yellow">(Lawyer Lee Jang-go)</font>

883
01:05:32,295 --> 01:05:35,369
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Lee Jang-go?</font>

884
01:05:38,053 --> 01:05:39,053
<font color="yellow">Jang-go?</font>

885
01:05:44,482 --> 01:05:45,724
<font color="yellow">Jang-go?</font>

886
01:06:03,767 --> 01:06:05,260
<font color="yellow">(Blow Breeze)</font>

887
01:06:05,451 --> 01:06:07,943
<font color="yellow">No! Where the heck did she go?</font>

888
01:06:08,302 --> 01:06:09,873
<font color="yellow">Your daughter is coming, too, right?</font>

889
01:06:09,898 --> 01:06:11,823
<font color="yellow">Why is she so interested in Hee-Ra?</font>

890
01:06:11,848 --> 01:06:14,084
<font color="yellow">There was this crazy psycho in the parking lot.</font>

891
01:06:14,109 --> 01:06:15,130
<font color="yellow">Crazy psycho?</font>

892
01:06:15,155 --> 01:06:17,873
<font color="yellow">He blocked me so that I couldn't even move!</font>

893
01:06:17,898 --> 01:06:20,224
<font color="yellow">I have no choice but to get the money from your husband.</font>

894
01:06:20,249 --> 01:06:22,380
<font color="yellow">I'll pay you back this week along with the interest.</font>

895
01:06:22,405 --> 01:06:24,786
<font color="yellow">-Let go! -What are you doing to my friend?</font>

896
01:06:24,811 --> 01:06:27,689
<font color="yellow">Jang-go. Fish boy, it's me.</font>

897
01:06:28,670 --> 01:06:29,912
<font color="yellow">Get on. I'll give you a ride.</font>

898
01:06:29,937 --> 01:06:31,935
<font color="yellow">If you don't eat, you'll become a fish.</font>

899
01:06:31,960 --> 01:06:34,927
<font color="yellow">Kim Seung-hee. You're Seung-hee, aren't you?</font>

